title: Anvar Bikzhanov
text:
Anvar Karimovich Bikzhanov (; born 21 April 1951) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> coach.
Bikzhanov has managed <a href="FC%20Lada-Togliatti-VAZ%20Togliatti">FC Lada-Togliatti-VAZ Togliatti</a> and <a href="FC%20Chernomorets%20Novorossiysk">FC Chernomorets Novorossiysk</a> in the <a href="Russian%20First%20Division">Russian First Division</a>.
